OL,4,CGhent Altarpiece: Prized Van Eyck oil
OL,5,Cpainting finds new home
OL,6, Art lovers will have even better access
OL,7, to the famous Ghent Altarpiece thanks
OL,8, to a 30m euro (#26m) upgrade to the
OL,9, Belgian cathedral where it is housed.
OL,11,FThe painting has been moved to a new
OL,12,Farea of St Bavo's Cathedral to create a
OL,13,F"revolutionary" visitor experience.
OL,15,FCompleted by Hubert and Jan Van Eyck in
OL,16,F1432, the painting has captivated the
OL,17,Fart world for centuries.
OL,19,FA seven-year, 2.2m euro (#1.8m)
OL,20,Frestoration project was completed in
OL,21,FDecember 2019.
